\c 84 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 84\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Gara Mana Waaqayyoo Yaaduu
\m (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; kun kiraara guddaadhaan yookiis akka qooqa faarfannaa kanaan dura beekame tokkootti faarfatame; faarfannaa ilmaan Qoraahi)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo gooftaa maccaa, iddoon buufata kee maal maal namatti tolaa! 
\m \bd 2\bd* Lubbuun koo oobdii mana Waaqayyoo yaaddee in gaggabdi! Lubbuun koo fi foon koo Waaqayyo isa jiraataatti gammadanii in ililchu.
\m \bd 3\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo gooftaa maccaa, mootii ko Waaqayyo kos, iddoo aarsaa keetti dinbiitiin illee mana, girrifnis mann'ee cuucota ishee keessa kaa'attu argatte;
\m \bd 4\bd* warri mana kee keessa jiraatanii, yeroo hundumaas jajuu kee faarfatan haa gammadan.
\m \bd 5\bd* Namoonni gara mana keetti adeemuu garaa keessaa qabaatanii si biraa humna argatan, haa gammadan!
\m \bd 6\bd* Isaan yeroo dachaa gogee nama boossisu keessa adeeman, iddoo sana lafa bishaan burqu in godhatu; bokkaan inni dura roobus eebba isa irra in diriirsa.
\m \bd 7\bd* Isaan caalaa humna godhachaa in adeemu, tulluu Xiyoon gubbaatti fuula Waaqayyoo duratti in argamu. 
\m \bd 8\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo gooftaa maccaa, kadhata koo anaaf dhaga'i, yaa Waaqayyo isa kan Yaaqoob, gurra kee as qabi.
\m \bd 9\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, gara gaachana keenyaa ilaali, fuula isa dibdee moosiftees ilaali!
\m \bd 10\bd* Iddoo biraa guyyaa kuma tokko ooluu irra, oobdii kee keessa guyyaa tokko ooluu wayya; godoota jal'inaa keessa taa'uu koo irra, balbala mana Waaqayyo koo dura ijaajjuu nan fo'adha.
\m \bd 11\bd* Waaqayyo gooftaan biiftuu dha, gaachanas; inni ayyaana, ulfinas in kenna; gooftichi wanta gaarii ta'e warra balleessaa malee deddeebi'an duraa hin hambisu.
\m \bd 12\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo gooftaa maccaa, namni si amanatu gammachuu attamii qaba!
\b 
